361
00:22:56,179 --> 00:22:58,249
Manager Xi, go get some water.

362
00:22:58,250 --> 00:22:59,199
Yes.

363
00:22:59,200 --> 00:23:00,900
Come here, too.

364
00:23:02,010 --> 00:23:03,510
