367
00:23:28,490 --> 00:23:30,490
Everyone, please have a look at these.

368
00:23:31,410 --> 00:23:34,730
My dear, it's still early to celebrate.

369
00:23:34,730 --> 00:23:36,959
Today, we sent out plenty of receipts.

370
00:23:36,960 --> 00:23:39,609
