398
00:25:19,040 --> 00:25:20,559
It's our Su's family business.

399
00:25:20,560 --> 00:25:23,530
It's none of your business.

400
00:25:27,560 --> 00:25:29,060
Tan'er,

401
00:25:30,320 --> 00:25:32,880
