415
00:26:10,310 --> 00:26:13,649
Your Worship, not even the good judge can settle family affairs.

416
00:26:13,650 --> 00:26:16,530
But what Su Wen Xing did is not technically family affairs.

417
00:26:16,530 --> 00:26:19,109
