- Catch him.

421
00:26:24,770 --> 00:26:27,109
Your Worship, Your Worship. It's not me. Seriously.

422
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:28,249
Your Worship.

423
00:26:28,250 --> 00:26:32,069
It's him. It's him.

